# Tor Relay Configuration — Non-exit relay
# Contributes bandwidth to the Tor network

ORPort 9001
DirPort 9030
ExitRelay 0
ExitPolicy reject *:*

Nickname CommonCloudRelay
ContactInfo tor@cloudpublica.org

# Data directory for keys and state
DataDirectory /var/lib/tor

# Logging
Log notice stdout

# Optional bandwidth limits (uncomment to cap relay bandwidth)
# RelayBandwidthRate 5 MBytes
# RelayBandwidthBurst 10 MBytes
